#

Loaded Potato Skins

40 min
$10
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyPork

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerSnackComfort Food

Description

Crispy potato skins topped with melted cheese, crispy bacon, and fresh green onions, perfect for a savory snack or appetizer!

Ingredients

  • russet potatoes: 4 large
  • cheddar cheese: 1 cup shredded
  • bacon: 1/2 cup cooked and crumbled
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • green onions: 1/4 cup chopped
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
